trans-unit.source: It is based on code provided at http://trac.turbogears.org/turbogears/ticket/255
This widget is an implementation of the interpreter example from MochiKit code. It is provided as a facility to develop TurboGears applications that needs JavaScript.
trans-unit.target: 这个小部件是MochiKit代码中解释器例子的实现。它是作为开发需要JavaScript的TurboGears应用程序的工具而提供的。
